[{"Code":"en","Title":"Activate payment channels","Slug":"activate-payment-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"cdf06b1b-70c1-4022-bd3b-86a2aa1683a6\">Find out which payment channels you can use based on your business entity type in the table below. You can use filter or search to find information about specific payment channels.</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appYc7UnQq5CmKe0G/shrlV9Nv97iK3QLdx\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\"></iframe></p><h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">Activation methods (applicable after <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">account verification</a>)</h3><ul data-block-id=\"be05b008-1a48-4365-b83f-81a833691c43\"><li data-block-id=\"262fddc8-ad57-40fd-aef4-3771bb08ba6e\"><p data-block-id=\"a68edbe4-f7a2-4c51-9739-5d68c283d699\">Instant - Available immediately after your account has been verified</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c46931c6-fd35-42f2-87c9-bd0ef4a5cd20\"><p data-block-id=\"6014b5f0-bba3-430a-a4f7-eb81a0907312\">Dashboard - Available by request on Xendit dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49b3e1d3-0e26-486a-8118-336fea4834e4\"><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">Contact CS - Available by request to help@xendit.co</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"93068e16-7e97-4974-ac06-d91067cb3136\"><strong>How to activate payment channels on Xendit dashboard</strong></h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"29934cad-8da2-41a5-8b02-f02a3588a877\"><p data-block-id=\"28b2334e-e001-4690-8561-214a1393e700\">Log in to your <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/\" translate=\"no\">Xendit dashboard</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">Click <strong>Payment Channels</strong> on your sidebar</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">Click <strong>Activate Payment Channels</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3789bc10-032d-4159-b311-c0915a0e0a47\"><p data-block-id=\"a9d07d1a-3caa-4955-a2e4-ed9ccbccaf8b\">Select the payment channels you’d like to activate</p></li><li data-block-id=\"44375777-970c-4e34-80d9-19ffe5d16cc0\"><p data-block-id=\"fa063204-f00d-4889-8261-18dd126f7416\">Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the process</p></li></ol><blockquote data-block-id=\"5129908d-3aa0-4922-a9f5-e0db69fc5edd\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"d2c017e9-e1fe-40a4-96bd-827419ee196f\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Note:</span></p></div><ul data-block-id=\"f9fe0f4e-91ef-417f-b4e4-8011c4fb4872\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Some payment channels may require additional documentation or verification</span></p><ul data-block-id=\"mbuaquud-glypvw-052\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong>Kredivo</strong> requires an additional User Acceptance Testing (UAT) process after you submit an activation request. You’ll need to complete this UAT to accept Kredivo transactions. Please refer to </span><a href=\"/v1/docs/kredivo-uat\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Kredivo UAT</span></a><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\"> for detailed steps.</span></p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"d59e0b54-e76f-4d26-9295-14a6f7291e37\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;\"><p data-block-id=\"699bc9db-2b7f-479b-a1d8-ba0083fca881\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Some payment channels might not be available for certain industries</span></p></li></ul></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mbuaqzic-2a8129-053\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Activate payment channels","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Aktifkan channel pembayaran","Slug":"activating-payment-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"cdf06b1b-70c1-4022-bd3b-86a2aa1683a6\">Cari tahu channel pembayaran mana yang dapat Anda gunakan berdasarkan jenis entitas bisnis Anda di tabel di bawah ini. Anda dapat menggunakan filter atau penelusuran untuk menemukan informasi tentang channel pembayaran tertentu.</p><p data-block-id=\"8e5decc6-2fc7-4ea2-8213-617d168e9707\"><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appYc7UnQq5CmKe0G/shrlV9Nv97iK3QLdx\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\"></iframe></p><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"5129908d-3aa0-4922-a9f5-e0db69fc5edd\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"d2c017e9-e1fe-40a4-96bd-827419ee196f\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\" type=\"spanMark\">Nota:</span></p></div><ul data-block-id=\"f9fe0f4e-91ef-417f-b4e4-8011c4fb4872\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\" type=\"spanMark\">Beberapa channel pembayaran mungkin memerlukan dokumentasi atau verifikasi tambahan</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"d59e0b54-e76f-4d26-9295-14a6f7291e37\"><p data-block-id=\"699bc9db-2b7f-479b-a1d8-ba0083fca881\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\" type=\"spanMark\">Beberapa channel pembayaran mungkin tidak tersedia untuk industri tertentu</span></p></li></ul></blockquote><h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">Metode aktivasi (berlaku setelah <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">verifikasi akun</a>)</h3><ul data-block-id=\"be05b008-1a48-4365-b83f-81a833691c43\"><li data-block-id=\"262fddc8-ad57-40fd-aef4-3771bb08ba6e\"><p data-block-id=\"a68edbe4-f7a2-4c51-9739-5d68c283d699\">Instan - Tersedia segera setelah akun Anda diverifikasi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c46931c6-fd35-42f2-87c9-bd0ef4a5cd20\"><p data-block-id=\"6014b5f0-bba3-430a-a4f7-eb81a0907312\">Dasbor - Tersedia berdasarkan permintaan di dasbor Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49b3e1d3-0e26-486a-8118-336fea4834e4\"><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">Hubungi CS - Tersedia berdasarkan permintaan untuk help@xendit.co</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"93068e16-7e97-4974-ac06-d91067cb3136\"><strong>Cara mengaktifkan channel pembayaran di dasbor Xendit</strong></h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"29934cad-8da2-41a5-8b02-f02a3588a877\"><p data-block-id=\"28b2334e-e001-4690-8561-214a1393e700\">Masuk ke <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/\" translate=\"no\">Xendit dashboard</a> Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">Klik <strong>Channel Pembayaran</strong> di bar samping Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">Klik <strong>Aktifkan Channel Pembayaran</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3789bc10-032d-4159-b311-c0915a0e0a47\"><p data-block-id=\"a9d07d1a-3caa-4955-a2e4-ed9ccbccaf8b\">Pilih channel pembayaran yang ingin Anda aktifkan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"44375777-970c-4e34-80d9-19ffe5d16cc0\"><p data-block-id=\"fa063204-f00d-4889-8261-18dd126f7416\">Ikuti petunjuk di layar untuk menyelesaikan proses</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"b8d53dff-cde7-42f3-b852-60961bf128f9\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Aktifkan channel pembayaran","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"เปิดใช้งานช่องทางการชำระเงิน","Slug":"activating-payment-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"cdf06b1b-70c1-4022-bd3b-86a2aa1683a6\">ค้นหาช่องทางการชำระเงินที่คุณสามารถใช้ได้ตามประเภทนิติบุคคลทางธุรกิจของคุณในตารางด้านล่าง คุณสามารถใช้ตัวกรองหรือค้นหาเพื่อค้นหาข้อมูลเกี่ยวกับช่องทางการชำระเงินที่เฉพาะเจาะจงได้</p>\n\n<p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appYc7UnQq5CmKe0G/shrlV9Nv97iK3QLdx\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p>\n\n<h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">วิธีการเปิดใช้งาน (ใช้ได้หลังจาก <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">การยืนยันบัญชี</a>)</h3>\n\n<ul data-block-id=\"be05b008-1a48-4365-b83f-81a833691c43\"><li data-block-id=\"262fddc8-ad57-40fd-aef4-3771bb08ba6e\"><p data-block-id=\"a68edbe4-f7a2-4c51-9739-5d68c283d699\">ทันที (Instant) - พร้อมใช้งานทันทีหลังจากที่บัญชีของคุณได้รับการยืนยันแล้ว</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c46931c6-fd35-42f2-87c9-bd0ef4a5cd20\"><p data-block-id=\"6014b5f0-bba3-430a-a4f7-eb81a0907312\">แดชบอร์ด (Dashboard) - พร้อมใช้งานเมื่อมีการร้องขอผ่าน Xendit dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49b3e1d3-0e26-486a-8118-336fea4834e4\"><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">ติดต่อ CS - พร้อมใช้งานเมื่อมีการร้องขอไปยัง help@xendit.co</p></li></ul>\n\n<h2 data-block-id=\"93068e16-7e97-4974-ac06-d91067cb3136\"><strong>วิธีเปิดใช้งานช่องทางการชำระเงินบน Xendit dashboard</strong></h2>\n\n<ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"29934cad-8da2-41a5-8b02-f02a3588a877\"><p data-block-id=\"28b2334e-e001-4690-8561-214a1393e700\">เข้าสู่ระบบ <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/\" translate=\"no\">Xendit dashboard</a> ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">คลิก <strong>Payment Channels</strong> บนแถบด้านข้างของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">คลิก <strong>Activate Payment Channels</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3789bc10-032d-4159-b311-c0915a0e0a47\"><p data-block-id=\"a9d07d1a-3caa-4955-a2e4-ed9ccbccaf8b\">เลือกช่องทางการชำระเงินที่คุณต้องการเปิดใช้งาน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"44375777-970c-4e34-80d9-19ffe5d16cc0\"><p data-block-id=\"fa063204-f00d-4889-8261-18dd126f7416\">ทำตามคำแนะนำบนหน้าจอเพื่อดำเนินการให้เสร็จสมบูรณ์</p></li></ol>\n\n<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"5129908d-3aa0-4922-a9f5-e0db69fc5edd\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"d2c017e9-e1fe-40a4-96bd-827419ee196f\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\" type=\"spanMark\">ข้อควรทราบ:</span></p></div><ul data-block-id=\"f9fe0f4e-91ef-417f-b4e4-8011c4fb4872\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\" type=\"spanMark\">ช่องทางการชำระเงินบางช่องทางอาจต้องใช้เอกสารหรือการยืนยันเพิ่มเติม</span></p><ul data-block-id=\"mbuaquud-glypvw-052\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\" type=\"spanMark\"><strong>Kredivo</strong> ต้องมีกระบวนการ User Acceptance Testing (UAT) เพิ่มเติมหลังจากที่คุณส่งคำขอเปิดใช้งาน คุณจะต้องดำเนินการ UAT นี้ให้เสร็จสมบูรณ์เพื่อรับธุรกรรม Kredivo โปรดดู </span><a href=\"/v1/docs/kredivo-uat\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\" type=\"spanMark\">Kredivo UAT</span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px\" type=\"spanMark\"> สำหรับขั้นตอนโดยละเอียด</span></p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"d59e0b54-e76f-4d26-9295-14a6f7291e37\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px\"><p data-block-id=\"699bc9db-2b7f-479b-a1d8-ba0083fca881\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\" type=\"spanMark\">ช่องทางการชำระเงินบางช่องทางอาจไม่พร้อมใช้งานสำหรับบางอุตสาหกรรม</span></p></li></ul></blockquote>\n\n<p data-block-id=\"mbuaqzic-2a8129-053\"></p>","SeoTitle":"เปิดใช้งานช่องทางการชำระเงิน","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Activar canales de pago","Slug":"activate-payment-channels","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"cdf06b1b-70c1-4022-bd3b-86a2aa1683a6\">Descubra qué canales de pago puede usar según su tipo de entidad comercial en la siguiente tabla. Puede usar el filtro o la búsqueda para encontrar información sobre canales de pago específicos.</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appYc7UnQq5CmKe0G/shrlV9Nv97iK3QLdx\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\"></iframe></p><h3 data-block-id=\"97ce409f-6fd8-408a-9a18-6a52a8d8ed7c\">Métodos de activación (aplicables después de la <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account#how-to-verify-your-business\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">verificación de cuenta</a>)</h3><ul data-block-id=\"be05b008-1a48-4365-b83f-81a833691c43\"><li data-block-id=\"262fddc8-ad57-40fd-aef4-3771bb08ba6e\"><p data-block-id=\"a68edbe4-f7a2-4c51-9739-5d68c283d699\">Instantáneo - Disponible inmediatamente después de que su cuenta haya sido verificada</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c46931c6-fd35-42f2-87c9-bd0ef4a5cd20\"><p data-block-id=\"6014b5f0-bba3-430a-a4f7-eb81a0907312\">Dashboard - Disponible a solicitud en el dashboard de Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49b3e1d3-0e26-486a-8118-336fea4834e4\"><p data-block-id=\"fa03c8ca-aa05-47f8-b7bc-c3f20b1b8283\">Contactar a CS - Disponible a solicitud a help@xendit.co</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"93068e16-7e97-4974-ac06-d91067cb3136\"><strong>Cómo activar canales de pago en el dashboard de Xendit</strong></h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"29934cad-8da2-41a5-8b02-f02a3588a877\"><p data-block-id=\"28b2334e-e001-4690-8561-214a1393e700\">Inicie sesión en su <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/\" translate=\"no\">dashboard de Xendit</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">Haga clic en <strong>Payment Channels</strong> en su barra lateral</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">Haga clic en <strong>Activate Payment Channels</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3789bc10-032d-4159-b311-c0915a0e0a47\"><p data-block-id=\"a9d07d1a-3caa-4955-a2e4-ed9ccbccaf8b\">Seleccione los canales de pago que desea activar</p></li><li data-block-id=\"44375777-970c-4e34-80d9-19ffe5d16cc0\"><p data-block-id=\"fa063204-f00d-4889-8261-18dd126f7416\">Siga las instrucciones en pantalla para completar el proceso</p></li></ol><blockquote data-block-id=\"5129908d-3aa0-4922-a9f5-e0db69fc5edd\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"d2c017e9-e1fe-40a4-96bd-827419ee196f\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Nota:</span></p></div><ul data-block-id=\"f9fe0f4e-91ef-417f-b4e4-8011c4fb4872\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Algunos canales de pago pueden requerir documentación o verificación adicional</span></p><ul data-block-id=\"mbuaquud-glypvw-052\"><li data-block-id=\"5549e812-d129-4787-917a-f942e4ddd33d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"0fa60435-3ec4-486b-bf58-9b37ae20c51f\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong>Kredivo</strong> requiere un proceso adicional de Pruebas de Aceptación del Usuario (UAT) después de enviar una solicitud de activación. Necesitará completar este UAT para aceptar transacciones de Kredivo. Por favor, consulte </span><a href=\"/v1/docs/kredivo-uat\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Kredivo UAT</span></a><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\"> para conocer los pasos detallados.</span></p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"d59e0b54-e76f-4d26-9295-14a6f7291e37\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:14px;\"><p data-block-id=\"699bc9db-2b7f-479b-a1d8-ba0083fca881\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">Algunos canales de pago podrían no estar disponibles para ciertas industrias</span></p></li></ul></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mbuaqzic-2a8129-053\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Activar canales de pago","Description":null}]